venue.name: MIT Killian Court

item.description:
New location.
MIT Killian court is located at the north east corner of Massachusetts ave and Memorial Dr, Cambridge. For those who take T should get off Red line at the Kendal station. Hope to see you tomorrow.

No-shows (you know who you are!) will NO longer be tolerated as demands are high and spaces are limited. Please DON'T RSVP YES unless you are absolutely sure you can make it.

This will be an "intermediate and up" level meetup. It will be outdoors on a grass field.

Intermediate level means: Players with firm understanding of game strategy. Should have a good grasp of skills (passing, setting, hitting) and be able to move around to cover areas of the court.


Terri
item.name: Intermediate Level at MIT Killian Court
